items.title: MS downgrades McDonald’s on limited upside and structural pressures on fast food
items.description: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley downgraded McDonald’s (NYSE:MCD) Corp to Equal-weight from Overweight, saying the fast-food giant’s stock already reflects much of its near-term improvement, while longer-term challenges remain.
